  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play][When Digivolving] By placing 1 Digimon card with
    the [X Antibody] or [Royal Knight] trait from your trash as this Digimon''s bottom
    digivolution card, all of your opponent''s play cost 10 or higher Digimon can''t
    attack players until the end of their turn.[All Turns][Once Per Turn] When an
    effect would remove this Digimon from the battle area, by returning 1 card with
    the [X Antibody] or [Royal Knight] trait from this Digimon''s digivolution cards
    to the bottom of the deck, prevent that removal.'
